	   <tr><td colspan=2>Doesn't Shard of Knight have a proc on it?&nbsp;&nbsp;I thought that it has a very nasty proc (but could be thinking of another new piercer).  If it proc's like I think it does, it's an Agro magnet that would be inappropriate for alot of raid situations so may be less appealing to you.  You have a nice set of weapons now so you really don't &quot;need&quot; the piercer if you don't have the skill to use it.<br><br>As for value, the Shard of Night is going for about 15-20k on Veeshan when it's sold (which is rarely) and the Shield goes for about the same and it's sold more often.  So from a monetary standpoint it sounds like a fair deal.  And if you get a Silvery Belt of Contention (about 7k on Veeshan now) you will end up with a comparable stats belt (yes a  little less haste) plus all the other nice stuff and be way ahead.<br><br>I have maxed piercing skills and would make the trade, but as I said it's probably not going to be useable for most raids.  The one question I really have is what's the graphics for it?  I hope it's not a FS Dagger look.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 55 DE Revenant<br>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 60 DE Gravelord</td></tr>
