	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would dump all points into STA.&nbsp;&nbsp;85 INT is fine--it wont materially hinder you if you don't put any points into it.<br><br>STA is probably the hardest stat to increase, yet, is probably one of the most important to SKs as they are the 2nd best tanks in the game (next to PLD) &amp; maximizing HP is very important.  I made the mistake of not dumping any into STA &amp; I now wish that I did.<br><br>As far as not being able to wear plate--that really isnt that big an issue anyways.  Dreadscale armor is relatively easy to get a full set &amp; that will carry you to 50 easy.  Or you can just purchase Ry'Gorr armor if you dont want to do the DS quests.  After that, you can graduate to PoG or Noct armor.<br><br>Lunatic<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
