	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am lvl 12 currently and working on gaining exp in N. Ro.&nbsp;&nbsp;The problem I am having is that I feel like I'm not contributing to my groups while slaughtering Derv Scum.  I am hesitant to summon my wimpy pet because I'm still not comfortable with him.  I can't seem to be able to find a way to single pull at all and have twice now resulted in multiple pulls.  My spells are nothing but fizzlefests.  My melee is only good for about 20per damage.  Am I actually contributing anything?  How can I do more?  I know you've all experienced this at this stage, how do I become a better group member?<br><br>&nbsp;<br>The darkest of the dark...<br>The Dark Elf Shadow Knight ...<br>Uuuarius</td></tr>
