	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings fellow Knight:<br><br>The closest SK trainer would be found in the city of the gnomes (Akanon sp?), I'm betting.&nbsp;&nbsp;I'm assuming you are a human SK, so I don't know how much, if any, faction work you will have to do in order to train in that city.<br><br>As far as binding, you can either find someone who can bind you in Greater Fay or run into Kelethin and get bound by the Soulbinder.  Note - You can not bind yourself.  I suggest politely asking for a bind inside GF and offering to donate a token amount.  Usually, people are happy to help out.<br><br>Good hunting<br><br>Shrikke - Knight of Fear<br>Bristlebane<br>&nbsp;<br>Shrikke - Knight of Fear<br>Bristlebane</td></tr>
